<h2>soc.mtb.wtf</h2>
<p><p>Welcome to soc.mtb.wtf. I made this for myself, but signups will stay open as long as I can manage.</p>

<p>Origin of the name: mtb is my initials, so I bought mtb.wtf a while ago; soc stands for social or SoCal or socialism or whatever you want it to stand for.</p>

<p>This instance has no specific purpose right now. If most of the users want one, we can discuss it.</p>

<p>If anything, this instance cares about privacy. I modified the <a href="/terms">terms</a> to get rid of potentially worrisome ad-related parts. If you see anything else you don't like, I can change it again.</a>

<p>See <a href="/about/more">about</a> for more info and for rules.</p></p>
